{
  "texts": [
    "The system automatically translates the user's content into any other target language while he speaks and writes in his native tongue.",
    "A problem is when there is a shortage of data for a certain language.",
    "In an attempt to cover all languages, Meta AI introduced the No Language Left Behind (NLLB) (Costa-jussà,, et al. 2022) model.",
    "To effectively train AI models, it focuses on Page 11 of 46 36",
    "transforming low-resource languages into high-resource ones."
  ]
}